#      UNRELATED to MAX_SEGMENTS (identical 0x400 in both before/after builds)
#   2. edx=0x4000 (16,384 B), esi=0 — HASH_CAPACITY*8 = 2*1024*8 = 16,384 B exactly
#      (registry hash-table zero-fill, bootstrap.rs "4b. OPT-B" loop)
#   3. edx=0x1004 (4,100 B), esi=0  — FREE_LIST_CAPACITY*4 + 4 = 1024*4+4 = 4,100 B exactly
#      (free-list index-stack zero-fill, bootstrap.rs "4c" loop)
#   4. (a further memset elsewhere in the inlined chain, byte-identical before/after)
